                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2"><locus target="#26v"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1084JesusChrist"/> (center), <term key="angel"/> (right)</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#27r"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1099StMary"/> (right), <term key="angel"/> (left)</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d4"><locus target="#38r"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1005Crucifixion"/> , with <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/> (left) and <persName ref="PRS5695John"/> (right)</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d5"><locus target="#56v"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1035HolyMan"/>,<persName ref="PRS4585Georgeo"/> and the <term key="dragon"/> and Birutawit</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d6"><locus target="#57r"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1084JesusChrist"/> Enthroned, surrounded by the four living creatures and a patron protrate below</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d7"><locus target="#129v"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1062CoronationMary"/></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d8"><locus target="#160v"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1101GodFatherOrb"/> (on the right) gives something to a saint (left); an <term key="angel"/> blows a ram’s horn (lower right)</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d9"><locus target="#161v"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1049Resurrection"/> and the raising of Adam and Eve</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d10">
                    Decorative designs:
                    <locus target="#45v"/> (haräg);
                    <locus target="#1r #1v #13r #29r #31r #31v #32r #32v #47v #55r #68r #68v #74v #83r #90v #113v #116r #122v #141r"/> (multiple full stops);
                    <locus target="#8v #17r #26r"/> (full stops connected with alternating red and black dots);
                    <locus target="#37v #89r #148v #162v"/> (full stops between lines of red and black dots);
                    <locus target="#52v #62r #74r"/> (line of red and black dots)
                    </decoNote>
